  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink244-kilavi">veṟiyāṭaṟuṇintuḻi vilakkaluṟuntōḻi cevili kēṭkumāṟṟāṉ talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu.   </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante, who thwarts it when the Veṟi-dance has been decided upon, told the heroine in a way that the foster-mother could hear.
  
          
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink244">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi paṉmalar</l> 
<l>naṟuntaṇ cōlai nāṭukeḻu neṭuntakai</l>
<l>kuṉṟam pāṭā ṉāyi</l>
<l>ṉeṉpayañ ceyyumō vēlaṟkav veṟiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">

        <l>Ah, friend,</l>
        <l rend="space">if the Vēlaṉ priest does not sing of the hill</l>
        <l>of the paragon who has a town</l>
        <l>with cool groves fragrant with many flowers,</l>
        <l rend="space">what benefit is that Veṟi-dance to him?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
